# --- Dependencies (regenerable from cli/package-lock.json via `npm ci`) -------
cli/node_modules/
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# --- Generated wiki output (regenerable via `doqmentary assemble`) ------------
documents/**/wiki/

# --- Editor / IDE settings (personal, machine-specific) ----------------------
.vscode/

# --- Company-specific enterprise content (keep index + examples) --------------
# Real principles/decisions are private; only README.md and *.example.md ship.
enterprise/principles/*
!enterprise/principles/README.md
!enterprise/principles/*.example.md
enterprise/decisions/*
!enterprise/decisions/README.md
!enterprise/decisions/*.example.md
